OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772478694
OL,3,CCouncil leader says plans to demolish
OL,4,C300 homes key to solving poor housing
OL,6,FThe leader of Blackpool Council says
OL,7,Fcontroversial plans to demolish 300
OL,8,Fhomes for a new regeneration project
OL,9,Fis vital to solving the town's poor
OL,10,Fhousing problems.
OL,12,FDuring a pre-budget speech, Councillor
OL,13,FLynn Williams highlighted the plans to
OL,14,Fbulldoze around 300 homes in Revoe as
OL,15,Fone of the Council's key means of
OL,16,Fimproving the town for residents and
OL,17,Fincreasing the quality of available
OL,18,Fhomes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772478694
OL,3,CCouncil leader says plans to demolish
OL,4,C300 homes key to solving poor housing
OL,6,FThe council is looking to use a #90m
OL,7,Fgrant to demolish the homes and
OL,8,Freplace them with modern housing.
OL,10,FCllr Williams said she does not "take
OL,11,Flightly" how disruptive the removal of
OL,12,Fpeople's homes and businesses will be,
OL,13,Fbut promised locals will receive the
OL,14,Fsupport they need.
OL,16,FA number of residents have hit out
OL,17,Fagainst the plans, with locals arguing
OL,18,Fthe money should be spent on improving
OL,19,Fthe existing homes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772478694
OL,3,CCouncil leader says plans to demolish
OL,4,C300 homes key to solving poor housing
OL,6,FCommunity leaders argue this would
OL,7,Fprevent families and locals from
OL,8,Fhaving their lives uprooted.
OL,10,FThe Reverend Matt Lockwood, of Beacon
OL,11,FChurch on Read's Avenue, is one of the
OL,12,Fscheme's fiercest critics and called
OL,13,Fit a "mass dispersion" of vulnerable
OL,14,Fpeople.
OL,16,FHe said many residents were anxious
OL,17,Fand fearful of the plans, which are
OL,18,Fexpected to go before Blackpool's
OL,19,Fplanning committee within the next few
OL,20,Fweeks.
OL,26,@uD@FOUuD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772478694
OL,3,CCouncil leader says plans to demolish
OL,4,C300 homes key to solving poor housing
OL,6,FHowever, Cllr Williams reiterated that
OL,7,Fthe overall quality of housing in
OL,8,FBlackpool remains too poor and
OL,9,Furgently needs to be addressed,
OL,10,Fsaying: "Our number one ambition is to
OL,11,Fprovide a quality, affordable home for
OL,12,Feveryone in Blackpool, building
OL,13,Fcommunities that our residents our
OL,14,Fproud to be part of.
OL,16,F"This is why the transformation of
OL,17,FRevoe is so vital to us and the future
OL,18,Fof the town ` the result of one of the
OL,19,Ffirst 'masterplans' developed with the
OL,20,Fcommunity.
OL,26,@rD@IOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772478694
OL,3,CCouncil leader says plans to demolish
OL,4,C300 homes key to solving poor housing
OL,6,F"In this first phase, we are talking
OL,7,Fabout the removal of people's homes
OL,8,Fand businesses, and we do not take
OL,9,Fthis lightly ` and those people and
OL,10,Fbusinesses will get the support they
OL,11,Fneed.
OL,13,F"But this investment, and the way it
OL,14,Fwill be delivered, is a once in a
OL,15,Flifetime opportunity to introduce
OL,16,Flight, space and quality in to an area
OL,17,Fof Central Drive ` which by its very
OL,18,Fname tells you how important it has
OL,19,Fbeen to Blackpool over the years `
OL,20,Fthat desperately needs it.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
