PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772478694
OL,3,CCouncil leader says plans to demolish
OL,4,C300 homes key to solving poor housing
OL,6,F"This intervention will deliver the
OL,7,Fcatalyst for the kind of investment
OL,8,Fthat the whole inner area needs to
OL,9,Fdeliver better housing quality,
OL,10,Favailability and sustainability, cheek
OL,11,Fby jowl with the opportunities for
OL,12,Fbusinesses to deliver the kind of
OL,13,Fservices that a strong, stable
OL,14,Fcommunity needs."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
