PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772478694
OL,3,CCouncil leader says plans to demolish
OL,4,C300 homes key to solving poor housing
OL,6,FCllr Williams said the council had
OL,7,Falready delivered 418 new council
OL,8,Fhomes, in Grange Park, Mereside and
OL,9,FQueens Park and this year would see a
OL,10,Fnew sheltered housing scheme open on
OL,11,FWhitegate Drive and new council homes
OL,12,Fcompleted in Bispham.
OL,14,FAt a Revoe residents' meeting last
OL,15,Fmonth, organised by Rev Lockwood,
OL,16,Fpeople worried about the plans were
OL,17,Foffered help by a national community
OL,18,Funion group.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
