FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772478694
OL,3,CCouncil leader says plans to demolish
OL,4,C300 homes key to solving poor housing
OL,6,FAlana Cooper, of Acorn Union, said:
OL,7,F"We believe refurbishment of existing
OL,8,Fhomes is possible, without the need
OL,9,Ffor demolition and we can get that
OL,10,Fmessage across."
OL,12,FBlackpool South MP Chris Webb has
OL,13,Fadded his voice to concerns about
OL,14,Fplans to demolish hundreds of homes in
OL,15,Fthe town's deprived Revoe area.
OL,17,FHe said: "It's clear that Revoe and
OL,18,Fthe Central Drive area is in need of
OL,19,Fregeneration and if done properly it
OL,20,Fwill improve housing quality, health
OL,21,Foutcomes and provide opportunity.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@PO]yD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772478694
OL,3,CCouncil leader says plans to demolish
OL,4,C300 homes key to solving poor housing
OL,6,F"I support the ambition to improve and
OL,7,Fcreate a more sustainable future for
OL,8,Fthis long neglected area.
OL,10,F"But regeneration can't come at an
OL,11,Funacceptable human cost and the people
OL,12,Fwho live in these streets should not
OL,13,Fbe treated as obstacles to progress `
OL,14,Fthey are Blackpool residents who
OL,15,Fdeserve fairness, dignity and proper
OL,16,Fsupport.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
