FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772478694
OL,3,CCouncil leader says plans to demolish
OL,4,C300 homes key to solving poor housing
OL,6,F"Blackpool Council has reassured me
OL,7,Fthat it is committed to supporting
OL,8,Fresidents through the process and I am
OL,9,Fpressing the leadership of the Council
OL,10,Fto build trust with residents and
OL,11,Fensure no one is left feeling confused
OL,12,For pressured.
OL,14,F"Regeneration should lift communities
OL,15,Fup, not displace them without
OL,16,Fsecurity. Getting this right is
OL,17,Fessential."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@KO]
